data.description:
Welcome to this charming Cape Cod home in a peaceful neighborhood, offering three bedrooms for comfortable living. Step into a cozy haven where classic design meets modern convenience. The heart of the home is a spacious and inviting living area, perfect for both relaxation and entertaining.

The highlight of this property is the deck in the backyard, providing a delightful space for gatherings with family and friends. Picture yourself enjoying sunny afternoons or evening barbecues with a panoramic view of downtown Akron as your backdrop. It's a scenic setting that adds a touch of urban charm to your outdoor experiences.

Additionally, this home features a walk-out basement, adding convenience and versatility to your living space. Whether you envision it as a recreation room, home office, or extra storage, the basement offers endless possibilities to suit your lifestyle.

This Cape Cod home combines the warmth of a traditional layout with the appeal of modern amenities, making it a perfect retreat in a convenient location. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your home and enjoy the best of both worlds – a tranquil residential setting with easy access to the vibrant downtown Akron scene.
